item.title: Gamemodes
item.author: invalid@example.com (Comrade Jerkov)
item.dc:creator: Comrade Jerkov
item.content:encoded:
If you're adding lots of gamemodes to OW (as I expect you probably are), I'd like to politely and respectfully request that you don't include either Bombing Run and Double Domination. I really do hope they do NOT feature. If you went back to the original UT'99 DOM, that'd be fine IMO. But not those two. Those are probably the most suckitudinous game modes ever devised. 2k4 has ONS to make up for it, but...yeah. Suckitudinous game modes

Yet I expect none of the original game's gamemodes...

Gamemodes
